Paper: hep-th/9902185

Date: 1999-02-25

Title: On the Generalised Pauli--Villars Regularization of the Standard Model

Authors: M.N. Stoilov

Comments: 7 pages, harvmac

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B457 (1999) 311-313

We show that the regularization of the Standard Model proposed by Frolov andSlavnov describes a nonlocal theory with quite simple Lagrangian.